reviewText: Double Up: The Experience. This wakeboarding video includes wakeboarding action shot with 16-mm film from Colin Wright, Sam Owens, Luke Wulf, Rich Facciano, Greg Nelson, and more. Dedicated to the memory of Corey Kraut. From the makers of "Monkey on a String", 601 Film Group presents a 16mm film-adventure showcasing the Double UP Team and what happens while traveling the U.S. on the Double UP Experience.
